      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, carefully add a<strong> pizza base </strong>to the pan<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span>, pushing the dough out to the edge to help shape the crust</p><p>Tip: To pick up the pizza dough, gently flip it over the back of your hand to stop it ripping!</p><p>Add 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1/4]</span> of the <strong>pizza sauce </strong>to each pizza base and spread it evenly with the back of a spoon (be careful of the hot pan!) then cook the <strong>pizza base</strong> for 3-4 min or until the crust has started to puff up, then remove the heated tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> from the oven and slide the <strong>pizza bases </strong>onto the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
