            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Repeat this process for the remaining pizza base<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p><p>Tip: Make sure the pizzas don't overlap on the tray to avoid raw dough!</p><p>Top the pizza bases with the <strong>dried</strong> <strong>oregano</strong>, <strong>torn mozzarella</strong>, <strong>‘Nduja</strong>, <strong>chilli rounds </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>sliced pepper</strong> and <strong>basil leaves</strong></p><p>Drizzle the crusts with <strong>olive oil</strong>, then put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span>in the oven for 12-15 min or until the cheese has melted and the crust has puffed up and browned</p>",
