    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>rocket leaves </strong>to a bowl with the <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong>, 2 tbsp<strong> </strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and mix it all together – this is your <strong>balsamic rocket</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>pizzas</strong> with the<strong> balsamic rocket</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
